        "collapsible_tab_TbRiah": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Benefits",
            "content": "<p><strong>Sleep deeper, naturally.</strong> Our Good Night Spray blends pure lavender and chamomile, two botanicals clinically proven to <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\">reduce anxiety and improve sleep quality</a> across 65+ studies and nearly 8,000 patients. Just one spray activates similar calming brain receptors as prescription sedatives, without the side effects.</p><ul><li><strong>Lavender</strong></li></ul><p>Lavender's active compound linalool naturally activates your brain's calming GABA receptors, promoting deep relaxation and restful sleep. Used in hospitals worldwide, backed by <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\">65+ clinical studies</a>, and trusted for over 2,500 years.<br/></p><ul><li><strong>Chamomile</strong></li></ul><p>Nature's oldest sleep botanical, prescribed by Hippocrates, trusted by every civilization since. Chamomile's star molecule apigenin <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8553734/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8553734/\">binds directly to your brain's relaxation receptors</a>, calming your nervous system naturally, still powerful enough for adults who've tried everything.<br/></p><ul><li><strong>Blend</strong></li></ul><p>Our Good Night Spray blends pure lavender and chamomile, two botanicals <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\">clinically proven to reduce anxiety and improve sleep quality</a> across 65+ studies. Two natural compounds, two calming pathways, one spray. </p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HbbKet": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Benefits",
            "content": "<p><strong>Sleep deeper, naturally.</strong> Our Good Night Spray Formula made from pure lavender, chamomile, and valerian root , three botanicals <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\">clinically proven to reduce anxiety and improve sleep quality</a> across <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33086877/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33086877/\">65+ studies</a> and nearly 8,000 patients. Just one spray activates similar calming brain receptors as prescription sedatives, without the side effects.</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Lavender</strong></li></ul><p>Lavender's active compound linalool naturally activates your brain's calming GABA receptors, promoting deep relaxation and restful sleep. Used in hospitals worldwide, backed by <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655395/\">65+ clinical studies</a>, and trusted for over 2,500 years.<br/></p><ul><li><strong>Chamomile</strong></li></ul><p>Nature's oldest sleep botanical, prescribed by Hippocrates, trusted by every civilization since. Chamomile's star molecule apigenin <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8553734/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8553734/\">binds directly to your brain's relaxation receptors</a>, calming your nervous system naturally, still powerful enough for adults who've tried everything.</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Valerian Root</strong></li></ul><p>Used for centuries as nature's strongest sleep root. Valerian's active compound valerenic acid <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29035887/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29035887/\">directly enhances GABA activity in the brain</a>, reducing the time it takes to fall asleep and improving overall sleep depth. Backed by a <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33086877/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33086877/\">systematic review and meta-analysis</a> confirming its effectiveness, and shown to improve sleep quality in clinical trials.</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>The Blend</strong></li></ul><p>Our Good Night Spray Formula pure lavender, chamomile, and valerian root, three botanicals clinically proven to <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\" title=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23476690/\">reduce anxiety and improve sleep quality</a> across 65+ studies. Three natural compounds, three calming pathways, one spray.</p>",
